sudo nano /etc/sddm.conf.d/10-endeavouros.conf

Add bellow [THEME]

[X11]
DisplayCommand=/usr/share/sddm/scripts/Xsetup

[Wayland]
DisplayCommand=/usr/share/sddm/scripts/Xsetup

[XDisplay]
DisplayCommand=/usr/share/sddm/scripts/Xsetup

Then:
sudo nano /usr/share/sddm/scripts/Xsetup

#!/bin/sh
xrandr --output eDP-1 --rotate right
